data.description:
Nearly new home right across the street from the new Samsung Plant. 1 story home boasts 4 bedrooms plus a separate study. Plenty of room for an office, workout or homeschool room. Whatever your family needs. Outside you'll find a very large back patio for outdoor living or dining. No neighbors behind! Home has nice light finishes and an abundance of natural light. Bonus feature: Primary closet is connected to the laundry room. Washer, Dryer and refrigerator included. Community includes a playground area, picnic facilities and many hike/bike/walking trails and is adjacent to Taylor High school. 3.5 miles to growing downtown Taylor with coffee shops and BBQ joints. Just 18 miles to downtown Round Rock. Call this house your home today!

Renter pays all utilities. No smoking.
